<title type="html"><![CDATA[9/11 (Sun.) Second-hand smoke / Michelin Guide lists 38 starred restaurants in Taiwan this year (Host: Joyce)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=651&amp;p=676#p676"><![CDATA[
9/11 (Sun.) Second-hand smoke / Michelin Guide lists 38 starred restaurants in Taiwan this year (Host: Joyce)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:35 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:35-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />--------------------------------------------<br /><br />Session I: Second-hand smoke<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.nhsinform.scot/healthy-living/stopping-smoking/reasons-to-stop/second-hand-smoke">https://www.nhsinform.scot/healthy-livi ... hand-smoke</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1.Do you or your family members smoke? How much do you know about the tobacco epidemic? <br /><br />2.Do you have some tips for asking others not smoking around you?<br /><br />3.Manufacturers market e-cigarettes as tools for quitting or cutting down on smoking. Are e-cigarettes a safe alternative to smoking?<br /><br />4.Do e-cigarettes emit secondhand smoke? Is secondhand “smoke” from vaping harmful?<br /><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br />Session II: Michelin Guide lists 38 starred restaurants in Taiwan this year<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://focustaiwan.tw/society/202208300019">https://focustaiwan.tw/society/202208300019</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1.Michelin Guide lists 38 starred restaurants in Taiwan this year, are you planning to drop by? <br /><br />2.Are you willing to pay significantly more to eat in restaurants that have been awarded a Michelin star?<br /><br />3.What is a Michelin star and why does it matter? <br /><br />4.How do Michelin Stars actually affect the restaurant business?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=46353">Ellen Lu</a> — Mon Sep 05, 2022 2:17 pm</p><hr />
